{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回「毒人毒计」：燕南天醒来后发现身陷恶人谷，被哈哈儿、杜杀、李大嘴、屠娇娇、阴九幽等恶人围困。杜杀以追魂血手与燕南天交手，被折断手腕。燕南天暴怒之下毁屋追人，恶人四散。司马烟以孩子为饵诱燕南天入陷阱，燕南天虽识破木偶暗器却仍被暗算。屠娇娇假扮尸身偷袭得手，点中燕南天四大穴道。恶人们围住倒地的燕南天，争相要亲手杀他，各怀私心。全章展现恶人谷的阴险毒计与燕南天的刚烈豪迈，以及恶人之间的自私内斗。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好恶贼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜得不错！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，死鬼还魂了！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好女不跟男斗，我要脱衣裳了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，燕南天，李某且来和你较量较量！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过还是杜老大的功夫好，小弟不敢和老大争锋！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "你为何不逃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "杜某一生对敌，从未逃过！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "你居然敢和燕某一拼？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "正是！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "来得好！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "谷中可有江琴其人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "没有就是没有！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "我那孩子在何处？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "不……不知道，你杀了我吧！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "怜你也算是条硬汉，饶你一命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "此刻你饶我，片刻后我却不会饶你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "燕南天几时要人饶过？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先还我的孩子来，否则燕某将此谷毁得干干净净！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我看你们能躲到几时！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "好，好，燕大侠果然醒来了，这里有几位朋友，都在等着瞧瞧天下第一神剑的风采。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "这几位朋友，不知道燕大侠可认得么？哈哈，待在下引见引见，这位便是血手杜杀！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "二十年前，杜某便已见过燕大侠一面，只可惜那一次在下身有要事，来不及领教燕大侠的功夫。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "二十年前，我若不是看你才被南天大侠路仲远所伤，不屑与你动手，你又怎会活到今日？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "在下已活到今日，而且还要活下去，而燕大侠你却快要死了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "但燕大侠临死之前，还能笑得出来，这一点倒和我哈哈儿有些相似——哈哈，这一位便是不吃人头李大嘴，燕大侠可听说过么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "李大嘴怎地三句不离本行，我为你引见名满天下的燕大侠，你也该客气两句才对，怎地一张口就是要吃人肉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说燕大侠的肉好吃，这正是我李大嘴口中最最奉承的赞美之词，你们这些只会吃猪肉的俗人知道什么！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说起来，猪又脏又臭，的确没有人肉干净，我哈哈儿委实也要尝尝燕大侠的肉是何滋味，哈哈，却又怕燕大侠肉太粗了，哈哈哈……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你又不懂了，粗肉有粗肉的滋味，细肉有细肉的滋味，和尚肉有和尚肉的滋味，尼姑肉有尼姑肉的滋味，那当真是各有千秋，各有好处。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "和尚的肉你也吃过么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "嘿，吃得多了，最有名的一个便是五台山的铁肩和尚，我整整吃了他三天……吃名人的肉，滋味便似特别香些。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "你到底吃过多少人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "可数不清了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "谁的肉最好吃？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若论最香最嫩的，当真要数我昔日那老婆，她一身细皮白肉……哈哈，我现在想起来还要流口水。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好了好了，莫要说了，你们瞧燕大侠已气成如此模样……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是不可再让燕大侠生气，人一生气，肉便酸了，此乃我苦心研究所得，各位不可不知。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位便是不男不女屠娇娇……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "我方才还替燕大侠端过菜，倒过酒，燕大侠早已认得我了，还用你来介绍什么！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "哈哈儿怎地如此罗嗦，难道要将谷中的人全介绍给他不成，还不快些问话，问完了也好到阴间来与我作伴。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "text": "哈哈，阴老九做鬼也不甘寂寞，燕大侠既已来了，你还怕他不去陪你！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我等不及了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "text": "阴老九，拿开你的鬼手，被你的鬼手一摸，这肉还能吃么！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "你来动手也未尝不可，只是要快些。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢，我还有话问他！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "问呀，又没有人拦着你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕南天，你此番可是为着杜某才到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "你还不配！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "杜某不配，谁配？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "江琴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江琴？谁听说过这名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈，恶人谷中可没有这样的无名小卒。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这厮虽无名，但却比你们还要坏上十倍，只要你们将这厮交出，燕某今日便放过你们！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙极妙极，各位可听到燕大侠说的话了么？燕大侠说今日要饶了咱们，咱们还不赶紧谢谢。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位如此好笑么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "你此刻被咱们用十三道牛筋铁线捆住，又被杜老大点了四处穴道，你不求咱们饶你，反说要饶咱们，天下有比这更好笑的事么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "但我也不妨告诉你，谷中的确没有江琴这个人，你必定是被人骗了，那人想必是叫你来送死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "可笑你居然真的听信了那人的话，哈哈！燕南天活了这么大，不想竟像个小孩子！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，这厮中气又足了起来，莫非杜老大的点穴手法，已被他方才在暗中行功破去了？",
      "tone": "惊慌",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "text": "且慢，我有话说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "且慢，我有话说。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "我等与你有何仇恨，你要下此毒手？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "text": "恶人谷中，俱是万恶之徒，杀光了也不冤枉。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "不错，我万春流昔年确是恶人，但却早已改过自新，你为何还要杀我？……你凭什么还要杀我？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为何要多杀无辜？我为何不能容人改过？恶人谷虽尽是恶人，也并非全无改过自新之辈！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "text": "去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多杀无辜又有何用？燕南天呀燕南天，你二弟只有此一遗孤，你若不定下心神，熟思对策，你若还是如此暴躁，你二弟只怕就要绝后了，那时你纵然杀尽了恶人谷中的人，又有何用？……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕大侠，你好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "在下穿肠剑司马烟！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "text": "原来是你！原来你已来了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕大侠还未来，在下便已来了，但燕大侠近日的故事，在下已有耳闻，所以燕大侠一来，此间便已知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "text": "你凭什么认为燕某不敢杀你？这倒有些奇怪。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "两国相争，不斩来使。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "text": "你是谁的使者？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "在下奉命而来，要请问燕大侠一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "text": "可是有关那孩子？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "text": "孩子在哪里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "在下奉命来请问燕大侠，若是他们将孩子交回，又当如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "text": "这个……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕大侠是否可以立刻就走，永不再来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "text": "为了孩子，我答应你！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "一言既出！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "text": "燕某说出来的话，永无更改！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "好！燕大侠请随我来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_yan",
      "speaker_name": "司马烟",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "那孩子便在屋里，但望燕大侠抱出了孩子后，立刻原路退回，燕大侠乘来的马车，已在谷口相候。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孩子，你吃苦了！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好恶贼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此暗算，岂能奈何燕某，若是想要燕某的命，何妨出来动手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出来！我问你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！你们躲，我倒要看你们能躲到几时！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这臭孩子又有什么了不起，你要，就还给你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恶贼，还给你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小屠果然有两手，竟将这孩子弄睡着了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好有这孩子作人质，否则……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "李大嘴，你要作什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我瞧这女的尸身皮肉细嫩，倒和昔日我那老婆相似。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "但这尸身已死了好几天了呀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要保养得好，还是可以吃的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "好，你吃了她也好，这想必就是燕南天那厮的弟媳妇，你吃了她，也可替杜老大出口气。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给你吃吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "好，燕南天，算你狠，居然找到了咱们。但你莫忘了，孩子还在咱们手中，只要你追出来，哼哼！哈哈！哈哈！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二弟，我对不起你，我，我！……我非但不能妥为照顾你的孩子，甚至连……连你们的尸身……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但愿你从此安息。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 503,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕南天呀燕南天，如今可知道我的手段？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕南天，你只当方才真是你找着咱们的么？……哈哈，这不过是咱们的妙计而已，好叫你自己送上门来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕南天，你只当方才真是咱们怕了你么？哈哈，那只不过是咱们知道你必已难逃性命，又何苦费力与你动手！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们还等什么？难道还要等他再跳起来？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢！我出力最多，要杀他，该由我来动手才是。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是早听我的，他此刻早已死了，哪里还需费这许多手脚？我瞧你们还是让我动手吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行，你们不会杀人，一个杀不好他的肉就酸了，吃不得的，自然还是该我动手才是。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 548
    }
  ],
